    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The steadily increasing spacing is a bug, but the default is not to have all lines flush with the left side of the screen. If you do want that behaviour, you need to set `c.PromptManager.justify = False`. Otherwise, it tries to line the start of each line up with the line before.\n\nI'll look into the increasing spacing.\n"
